<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-white" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Exercise 2 -->
  <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="true">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
      Sottolinea forma attiva<span class="inline-block w-5 h-5 bg-yellow-300 rounded ml-1 cursor-pointer" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="yellow" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span> e forma passiva<span class="inline-block w-5 h-5 bg-green-300 rounded ml-1 cursor-pointer" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="green" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span>.
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4 cursor-pointer">
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        Ieri in classe <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">abbiamo festeggiato</span> l'arrivo di una nuova compagna: Lorena. Per l'occasione <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">abbiamo organizzato</span> anche una caccia al tesoro. Gli indizi <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="green">sono stati scritti</span> da Cristina e Emanuel, mentre il tesoro <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="green">è stato preparato</span> da Ryan e Giusy, gli "artisti" della classe. Lorena <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">ha indovinato</span> tutte le risposte e alla fine il tesoro <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="green">è stato trovato</span> dalla sua squadra.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Info Box Schema -->
  <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 p-4 md:p-6 pb-8 rounded-lg">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-4">
      <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Ecco lo schema per passare dalla forma attiva a quella passiva.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4">
      <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700">
        <p><span class="font-bold">•</span> Il <strong>soggetto</strong> della forma attiva diventa <strong>complemento d'agente</strong> (se è un animale o una persona) o <strong>complemento di causa efficiente</strong> (se è una cosa) della forma passiva;</p>
        <p><span class="font-bold">•</span> il <strong>complemento oggetto</strong> diventa <strong>soggetto</strong> della forma passiva.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 3 -->
  <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="true">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">3</span>
      Sottolinea complemento d'agente<span class="inline-block w-5 h-5 bg-blue-300 rounded ml-1 cursor-pointer" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="blue" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span> e complemento di causa efficiente<span class="inline-block w-5 h-5 bg-orange-300 rounded ml-1 cursor-pointer" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="orange" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span>.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg cursor-pointer">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Il pacco viene consegnato <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">dal corriere</span>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> La scritta fu cancellata <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="orange">dalla pioggia</span>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Il messaggio viene diffuso <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="orange">dalla radio</span>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Il cartellone fu colorato <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">dagli allievi</span>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 4 -->
  <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">4</span>
      Indica se la frase è di forma attiva o di forma passiva, poi scrivila nell'altra forma.
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 italic">
        Fai attenzione a mantenere i tempi verbali nel passaggio all'altra forma.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Lia accese il fuoco. → <strong class="text-green-700">f. attiva</strong></p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Il fuoco fu acceso da Lia. → <strong class="text-green-700">f. passiva</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 mb-2">
          <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Il premio viene ritirato dalla regista. → f.</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-24 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="passiva" data-correct-answer="passiva">
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <input type="text" class="flex-1 min-w-[250px] border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="La regista ritira il premio" data-correct-answer="La regista ritira il premio">
          <span class="text-gray-700">→ f.</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-24 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="attiva" data-correct-answer="attiva">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 mb-2">
          <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">I ragazzi hanno fondato una band. → f.</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-24 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="attiva" data-correct-answer="attiva">
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <input type="text" class="flex-1 min-w-[250px] border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="Una band è stata fondata dai ragazzi" data-correct-answer="Una band è stata fondata dai ragazzi">
          <span class="text-gray-700">→ f.</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-24 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="passiva" data-correct-answer="passiva">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-right text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
    Esercizi p. <%= link_to "172", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p172"), class: "text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800 underline" %>
  </div>

  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
</div>
